-- Sterigenics raises Nordion buyout offer to $758 mln
-- By Ashutosh Pandey in Bangalore
-- Mon May 05, 2014 07:20AM EDT
-- None



May 5 (Reuters) - Canadian medical isotopes supplier Nordion Inc <NDN.TO> <NDZ.N> said on Monday that Sterigenics, a sterilization services provider owned by private equity firm GTCR LLC, increased its offer price to $758 million from $727 million.

